	<p><blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>Thorzion</b><br /><i>True, but any mage will tell you in a hurry that pet canni is a downtime <i>only</i> tool.</i><hr size="1" /></blockquote>I was on an adventure with a friend who went from OOM to FM in two fights using pet canni. Granted they were fairly long fights but it was in only a few minutes. Suspend Minion 2 is pretty damn good for Mages-- stash your buffed and equipped pet and chain canni the others. Focus items are no problem since they have the full range of them available to themselves. It doesn't take nearly as long as you think.</p>
	
	
	
