	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>The agro on ALL dots, not just shm ones is way too high.  Ive have no problem being prolly the lowest dps class in the game other then clerics, but there is simply NO reason that dots should have more agro, worse resists and be less efficent then DDs.  And in just about every situation other then soloing they are.<br />
<br />
Bad things about DoTs:<br />
Once on keeps breaking mez<br />
ONLY if u are soloing are they more effiecent then DDs, mobs die too fast<br />
DDs get partial resists, Dots full resist (go see how often u land a DoT pvp on a well equipped person vs a DD)<br />
Agro is at least x3 more then a DD that does the same dmg (Try slow, bane, blood and see how often u tank)<br />
<br />
In my experience, except for soloing, DDs are better just about 99% of the time for these reasons.<br />
<br />
These are problems that all dots have not just shm ones.  Again I have no problem doing 1/4 the dps of a wiz, but I dont see why I should have to die from agro just to do that anemic amount of dmg.</p>
	
	
	
