	<p>This is what happens when SOE makes an expansion where soloing is impossible.  <br />
<br />
What was balanced? previously (dot aggro) is not so balanced now that its situational use has been backbenched.  Some spells are not supposed to be used in some situations.  Dots were great for soloing but now in LDON everyone has to group so dot functionality has taken a nose-dive.<br />
