	<p>I dont know if this is the "best possible DPS" but I found that on a bossmob I like too hit BoU early , then chain a few nukes . When BoU expires the first time I recast BoU then stick BoS as well . Lightly chain nukes while keeping both BoU and BoS on the bossmob . Then when the bossmob reaches 50% or so I continue too keep both dots running but I really open up with near constant chain nukes .<br />
I rarely get agro this way and it at least Feels like im doing good Damage .<br />
<br />
In exp groups it gets harder . I usualy Sick the hasted dog "starts my DPS early" Hit slow on the mob . Hit Bane on the mob "Adds too the DPS I started with my dog" . Generaly when bane lands the mob is already at 70%ish life . I then Acentuate the Damage I deal with a nice velium strike for puncuation .<br />
Hence in exp groups my Damage per mob "Best case" works out too be<br />
1. The dog beating on the mob from the start .<br />
2. Bane at 400 per tic "id say 4 ticks get out on avg" <br />
3. Vstrike at 925 or up too 1850 if im lucky .<br />
<br />
Totaly Damage per mob roughly .. 3kish too 4kish . Consistantly delt , pending resists ect .<br />
Again this SEEMS like good damage too me .</p>
	
	
	
	
	
